items.title: Nifty Financial Services in 'overbought' zone; PSU Bank eyeing pullback
items.description: Stock market trading strategy: The NIFTY PSU Bank Index is currently showing a downtrend in the near term, indicating a temporary pullback within its overall long-term bullish trend

items.title: 25 or 50: How much will the Fed cut rates to begin its policy easing cycle?
items.description: The FOMC meeting is widely expected to see policy rates reduced by 25 or 50 bps, but investors will also be looking at the Fed's commentary to determine the frequency and quantum of future rate cuts
